text: The 2016–17 season was Al-Nassr Football Club's 62nd in existence and 41st consecutive season in Pro League, the top flight of Saudi Arabian football. Along with Pro League, Al-Nassr competed in the Crown Prince Cup and King Cup. ==Players== ===Squad information=== ==Transfers== ===In=== ===Out=== ===On loan=== ==Pre-season friendlies==
